DESCRIPTION:Join the Arts & Culture Team for a chill and crafty block printing social at Café Red. Hand-carved stamp blocks\, ink\, blank stickers\, cards\, and bandanas provided. If you would like to slap some designs on a shirt or bag\, feel free to bring additional items you would like to customize with permanent block printed designs.
