SUMMARY:Ecosocialism and Green New Deal Working Group
DESCRIPTION:Join us biweekly for continued conversations about our vision and strategies for ecosocialist politics. Ecosocialism promotes democratic control over all institutions that impact life and the environment. A Green New Deal (GND) distills actions to address the climate crisis through a rapid and just transformation of these institutions. Questions? Please contact greennewdeal@seattledsa.org . \nRSVP here for zoom link.
URL:https://seattledsa.org/event/ecosocialism-and-green-new-deal-working-group-27/
LOCATION:Virtual\, WA\, United States
CATEGORIES:Ecosocialism,Green New Deal
GEO:47.7510741;-120.7401385
END:VEVENT
