DESCRIPTION:Join us for the Seattle DSA Arts & Culture Team bi-weekly meeting every other Tuesday at 6:30 PM. We will collaborate on ways for SDSA to engage in the local Arts & Culture scene\, and find opportunities to leverage our members’ artistic talents to advance socialism. RSVP for meeting link.
