LAST-MODIFIED:20260319T064057Z
UID:10018258-1775394000-1775401200@seattledsa.org
SUMMARY:Seattle DSA Fundraising Drive
DESCRIPTION:Join us on Sunday\, April 5th as we make calls to Seattle DSA members and ask them to make monthly contributions to help close our $8\,500 budget gap this year! \nSeattle DSA has been working hard this year to protect our neighbors\, promote progressive taxes\, and fight for a better world. Closing our budget gap will allow us to keep it up\, and exceeding our goals would allow us to act even more boldly.  \nYour friends and comrades are going to ask members who are currently giving monthly local donations to chip in a bit more each month. We’ll also be calling members who aren’t yet providing donations to the chapter and asking them to start.  \nYou’ll be provided a script and a list of people to call. If you’ve ever wondered how you can get people to buy into financially supporting grassroots projects\, this is a great place to start. \nBeacon Hill library branch\nLocated right by Beacon Hill Link station
URL:https://seattledsa.org/event/seattle-dsa-fundraising-drive/
LOCATION:Beacon Hill Branch – Seattle Public Library\, 2821 Beacon Ave S\, Seattle\, WA\, 98144\, United States
CATEGORIES:Finance and Fundraising Committee
GEO:47.5779493;-122.311379
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Beacon Hill Branch – Seattle Public Library 2821 Beacon Ave S Seattle WA 98144 United States;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=2821 Beacon Ave S:geo:-122.311379,47.5779493
END:VEVENT
