DESCRIPTION:Join DSA members statewide in working with DSA-endorsed Representative Shaun Scott in the state legislature. We meet weekly to develop and analyze policies designed to better serve Washington’s working class!
URL:https://seattledsa.org/event/washington-state-socialists-in-office-committee/2026-05-04/
CATEGORIES:New Member Friendly
