SUMMARY:Electoral Working Group Planning Subcommittee Meeting
DESCRIPTION:Help us brainstorm\, research\, and plan for future electoral campaigns! We’re currently working on planning a potential campaign for WA State House in the 37th LD. Some of the other tasks of this subcommittee include unified campaign ideation\, powermapping districts\, assessing required scale of mobilization (field\, fundraising\, etc.) for potential campaigns\, and candidate development and recruitment. \n\nSign up for our weekly calendar event that contains the Zoom link using the form below! Email electoral@seattledsa.org with any questions.
URL:https://seattledsa.org/event/electoral-working-group-planning-subcommittee-meeting-4-2-2-2/2026-05-11/
CATEGORIES:Electoral
LOCATION:
END:VEVENT
